title: Celsius claim Galaxy Digital seeking over $190,000 to repay $3 debt
description:
Celsius has objected to a motion filed by cryptocurrency company Galaxy Digital seeking over $190,000 in fees for storing only $2.67 worth of Celsius’ digital assets. In a bankruptcy court filing Thursday, Celsius argues that Galaxy’s services were not necessary expenses deserving priority repayment. Celsius filed for Chapter 11 bankruptcy protection in July.
